metadata.name: Endless smile ...
metadata.description:
An old lady in her 90s, from the local tribes of Xeldem village around Quepem, was seen volunteering the age-old traditional cooking style at the Tribal Festival of Goa. She had a smiling face since I was trying to take her photograph, until I took this shot of her getting engrossed in cooking. I was happy after taking this portrait as she had a endless smile ...
